Class ACCPersistenceArchivist

  • java.lang.Object

        • com.sun.enterprise.deployment.archivist.ACCPersistenceArchivist

  • @Service
public class ACCPersistenceArchivist
extends PersistenceArchivist
    PersistenceArchivist for app clients that knows how to scan for PUs in the app client itself as well as in library JARs (or top-level JARs from the containing EAR) that might accompany the app client.
